OL,3,CMajor supermarkets face call to
OL,4,Creinstate pay in line with real living
OL,5,Cwage
OL,7,FSupermarkets are being urged to
OL,8,Frestore worker pay in line with the
OL,9,Freal living wage after a raft stepped
OL,10,Fback from matching the salary
OL,11,Fbenchmark in recent years amid soaring
OL,12,Findustry cost pressures.
OL,14,FInvestor activists ShareAction is
OL,15,Fcalling on the UK's biggest grocery
OL,16,Fchains ` and some of the country's
OL,17,Fbiggest employers ` to reinstate pay
OL,18,Fat the level of the real living wage.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
