FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1775495152
OL,3,CMajor supermarkets face call to
OL,4,Creinstate pay in line with real living
OL,5,Cwage
OL,7,FPlayers in the sector announced pay
OL,8,Frises in recent weeks ahead of the
OL,9,FApril 1 increase in the national
OL,10,Fminimum wage, which rose to #12.71 per
OL,11,Fhour for those aged 21 and over across
OL,12,Fthe UK.
OL,14,FWhile many are paying shop workers
OL,15,Fabove the minimum wage, few now match
OL,16,Fthe higher real living wage ` a
OL,17,Fvoluntary independent industry
OL,18,Fdesigned to be calculated on the real
OL,19,Fcost of living, and is currently set
OL,20,Fat #13.45 an hour and #14.80 in London.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1775495152
OL,3,CMajor supermarkets face call to
OL,4,Creinstate pay in line with real living
OL,5,Cwage
OL,7,FM&S was revealed last month to be no
OL,8,Flonger offering pay in line with the
OL,9,Freal living wage when it announced its
OL,10,Flatest wage hike, despite a rise of at
OL,11,Fleast 6.4% and offering levels above
OL,12,Fthe national minimum wage and
OL,13,Finflation.
OL,15,FThe Co-operative Group also became the
OL,16,Flatest to announce its pay rise for
OL,17,Fworkers, with a 3.5% increase from
OL,18,FApril, but has now dropped a previous
OL,19,F"long-standing commitment" to the real
OL,20,Fliving wage.
OL,26,@{D@AOU{D@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
