OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1775495152
OL,3,CMajor supermarkets face call to
OL,4,Creinstate pay in line with real living
OL,5,Cwage
OL,7,FThe two biggest players in the sector
OL,8,F` Tesco and Sainsbury's ` also no
OL,9,Flonger match pay to the real living
OL,10,Fwage and have not since 2025.
OL,12,FBoth pay higher than the national
OL,13,Fminimum wage after above-inflation
OL,14,Frises, but not at the living wage
OL,15,Flevel.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
