CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1775495152
OL,3,CMajor supermarkets face call to
OL,4,Creinstate pay in line with real living
OL,5,Cwage
OL,7,FDiscount supermarkets Aldi and Lidl
OL,8,Fare the only major supermarkets to pay
OL,9,Fentry-level shop staff in line with
OL,10,Fthe real living wage nationwide, with
OL,11,FAldi's hourly rate exceeding the
OL,12,Fbenchmark.
OL,14,FThe John Lewis Partnership, which owns
OL,15,Fsupermarket Waitrose, has hiked shop
OL,16,Fstaff pay by 6.9% from April but only
OL,17,Fmatches the real living wage for
OL,18,Femployees within the M25.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
