FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1775495152
OL,3,CMajor supermarkets face call to
OL,4,Creinstate pay in line with real living
OL,5,Cwage
OL,7,FShareAction said pressure on firms to
OL,8,Fmake firm commitments on pay would be
OL,9,Fa "major focus" for it at upcoming
OL,10,Fannual meetings for shareholders.
OL,12,FBut it comes amid steep cost pressures
OL,13,Fon the sector, not least higher
OL,14,FNational Insurance contributions after
OL,15,Fthe tax hike in April last year.
OL,26,@qD@COUqD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1775495152
OL,3,CMajor supermarkets face call to
OL,4,Creinstate pay in line with real living
OL,5,Cwage
OL,7,FLouise Eldridge, head of good work at
OL,8,FShareAction, told the Press
OL,9,FAssociation: "It's disappointing to
OL,10,Fsee supermarkets like M&S, Sainsbury's
OL,11,Fand Tesco moving away from matching
OL,12,Fthe real Living Wage pay rates after
OL,13,Fsetting the pace in recent years.
OL,15,F"We know retailers are under real
OL,16,Fpressure.
OL,18,F"The latest Living Wage rise reflects
OL,19,Fhigher living costs, but that's
OL,20,Fexactly why paying people a wage they
OL,21,Fcan actually live on is so important."
OL,26,@qD@NOUwD@AOUzD@AOU}D@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1775495152
OL,3,CMajor supermarkets face call to
OL,4,Creinstate pay in line with real living
OL,5,Cwage
OL,7,FShe added: "Investors have been making
OL,8,Fthe case to these companies that
OL,9,Fbetter pay has proven business
OL,10,Fbenefits, from better morale to lower
OL,11,Fturnover and higher productivity.
OL,13,F"We've made progress on disclosure,
OL,14,Fbut that alone won't help staff cover
OL,15,Fthe basics, so we're continuing to
OL,16,Fpush for concrete commitments on pay.
OL,17,FThis will be a major focus for us at
OL,18,Fsupermarket AGMs this year."
OL,26,@oD@LOUuD@AOUzD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1775495152
OL,3,CMajor supermarkets face call to
OL,4,Creinstate pay in line with real living
OL,5,Cwage
OL,7,FA spokeswoman for Sainsbury's, which
OL,8,Fincreased worker pay by 5% in April,
OL,9,Fsaid the group had increased hourly
OL,10,Fwages by 42% in the past five years.
OL,12,F"Our colleagues are at the heart of
OL,13,Four success and rewarding them well
OL,14,Fcontinues to be a priority," she said.
OL,16,FA Co-op spokesperson said: "In recent
OL,17,Fyears we have aligned our lowest rates
OL,18,Fof pay with the Real Living Wage,
OL,19,Falthough we are not formally
OL,20,Faccredited as a Real Living Wage
OL,21,Femployer.
OL,26,@tD@AOUvD@\O]xD@\OU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
