OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1775495152
OL,3,CMajor supermarkets face call to
OL,4,Creinstate pay in line with real living
OL,5,Cwage
OL,7,F"Pay is considered as part of our
OL,8,Fwider reward offer, which includes
OL,9,Fbenefits such as paid breaks,
OL,10,Fcolleague discounts and wellbeing
OL,11,Fsupport."
OL,13,FM&S stressed it has never formally
OL,14,Fcommitted to the living wage.
OL,16,FTesco said its wages have risen by 43%
OL,17,Fover the last five years, adding its
OL,18,Fworkers "also benefit from a
OL,19,Fcompetitive reward package."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@IO]zD@IOU{D@\O]
